# Task Tracker App

A full-stack task tracker application built with **React (Vite)**, **ExpressJS**, and **MongoDB**, allowing users to:

-     Sign up / Login with JWT authentication
-  Create and manage up to 4 projects per user
- Add, update, and delete tasks under each project
-  Track task status (Pending, In Progress, Completed)

